<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<style>
  body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; padding: 40px; }
  .header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; border-bottom: 2px solid #ccc; padding-bottom: 10px; }
  .section { margin-top: 20px; }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 10px; }
  th, td { border: 1px solid #999; padding: 8px; text-align: left; }
  th { background-color: #eee; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h3>DAILY CONSTRUCTION REPORT</h3>
    <div>
      <p><strong>Date:</strong> 2024-02-12</p>
      <p><strong>Job Name:</strong> Project Alpha</p>
      <p><strong>Weather:</strong> Cloudy, 65°F</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h4>Personnel</h4>
    <table>
      <tr>
        <th>Name</th>
        <th>Trade</th>
        <th>Hours</th>
        <th>Task</th>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>John Smith</td>
        <td>Carpenter</td>
        <td>8</td>
        <td>Framing walls</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Jane Doe</td>
        <td>Electrician</td>
        <td>6</td>
        <td>Rough-in wiring</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Bob Wilson</td>
        <td>Laborer</td>
        <td>8</td>
        <td>Cleanup & Material moving</td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h4>Work Performed / Notes</h4>
    <p>Completed framing of north wall. Started electrical rough-in for office area. Site cleanup at end of day. No safety incidents.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h4>Equipment Used</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Forklift (4 hrs)</li>
      <li>Generator (8 hrs)</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
